# MTLFeatureSet.tvOS_GPUFamily2_v1

**Case**

The GPU family 2, version 1 feature set for tvOS.

## Declaration

```swift
case tvOS_GPUFamily2_v1
```

## Discussion

This feature set corresponds with Apple A10 devices running tvOS 11.

## tvOS GPU family 2

- **MTLFeatureSet.tvOS_GPUFamily2_v2**: The GPU family 2, version 2 feature set for tvOS.
